":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ac469c1d24","type":"paragraph","text":"重庆无产阶级工人造反军代表黄康发言：揭露李井泉收买8·15头头，镇压无产阶级文化大革命的滔天罪行。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bef8eda30c","type":"paragraph","text":"242代表发言：问有没有军委命令，撤销红总，楚平、韦杰答复（韦杰站起来不语）","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a22867441c","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：中央没有过。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"83e19ea2aa","type":"paragraph","text":"众呼：毛主席万岁！打倒韦杰，打倒甘渭汉！","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"52f76ccf50","type":"paragraph","text":"王力：刚才有同志提出，请韦杰副司令员答复，是不是中央军委有取缔后字242的命令？","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4428a4d375","type":"paragraph","text":"韦杰：这个命令没有，工程学院这个事情是军区党委研究的。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c2351e79b4","type":"paragraph","text":"问：为什么盗用中央军委命令？","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0a2b6aa25c","type":"paragraph","text":"韦杰：我们没有这样做，可能是军里没有听清（群众纷纷揭露他们盗用中央军委的名誉）","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3bcf6fa4df","type":"paragraph","text":"王力：天保放出来没有？（重庆代表揭露还有许多同志没有放出来，关在中美合作所监狱。）","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2870cb8e7c","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：韦副司令，你听到没有？马上释放。","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a707823514","type":"paragraph","text":"众呼：毛主席万岁！打倒韦杰！打倒甘渭汉！（重庆地区揭发）","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cbdfb38698","type":"paragraph","text":"王力：请大家简单点，四川的情况中央已经清楚了，重庆也很清楚。","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b050de8200","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：请乐山代表发言。（乐山代表发言略）","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8dd5a92fee","type":"paragraph","text":"十时十分总理、康生同志到会，会场高呼毛主席万岁！","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"61adde390a","type":"paragraph","text":"乐山代表谈昨天还抓了五人。","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"599cd4cdca","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：昨天还抓五个人吗？（大家要求发言）","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6bec6b8e86","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：大家心情激动是可以理解的，我们听不清，讲的慢一点，声音不要太大。","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"676039f4f4","type":"paragraph","text":"乐山代表：有一军分区支持的反动组织一面旗子还有江青同志的私章。","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"88c62133a5","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：我没有私章。","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a8bce47ce5","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：有个张家口军事学校的王行虎同志要求见中央军委，就这里谈吧！","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b59892eaa2","type":"paragraph","text":"王行虎：有人说，江青同志说：甘渭汉是好人，办了坏事，我决不相信江青同志能说这样的话。（江青笑了）","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f037d4b871","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：南充军分区司令员自己来揭发，好不好？（鼓掌）","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"41ce18aa4c","type":"paragraph","text":"南充：揭发对牛鬼蛇神，大扫除，要多抓，抓头头，这就是布署，南充代表谈到还有公安局和保守派的人来北京。","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f9bf5a9507","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：他们住在哪儿？","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3a4134527f","type":"paragraph","text":"南充：住西直门，具体住哪儿，他们不告诉我们。","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e4a51bbe01","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：把名单开来。现在谈万县问题。","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0edba8cddb","type":"paragraph","text":"万县代表：军分区用机枪扫射学生，最小的才六岁，叫举手，有一个学生提裤子被打了一枪，肠子打出来了，这学生临死前用手指沾血写了“我是革命的人”几个字。","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ebb7137a5c","type":"paragraph","text":"新北大万县调查组：韦杰在西苑旅社开黑会，四点指示：（一）原则坚持；（二）错误检查；（三）支左工作他们说错了，我们说对了；（四）总的由军区负责。","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"69077c8f40","type":"paragraph","text":"万县公安局打电话回去说：我们一到站就被包围了。因此，许多保字号组织打死人不下五十人，军分区第一次就打死五人，伤九人。","index":33,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"02389a971a","type":"paragraph","text":"万县的发了言。","index":34,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"383cbaa1a1","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：请涪陵的发言。","index":35,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"74254cd5cd","type":"paragraph","text":"广元部队：我是总参三部派往广元的部队，（1）绵阳军分区一月份突然增加了六个科；（2）二月二十一日军委（成都军区电报）说：这是绝密文件，内容：各部队修筑坚强工事准备一个月粮食设置指挥员。（3）调一个营到绵阳镇压造反派，部队打电话询问中央，军分区对他们大不满。（4）派人控制火车站，抓告状的，组织政法小组。","index":36,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"03855cd892","type":"paragraph","text":"十条以后，军分区派人去控制7012部队一个营。","index":37,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9099dcd7ab","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：今天开会到这儿，明天请梁新初司令员开个小会，大家谈谈。","index":38,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"be9d680e4f","type":"paragraph","text":"林跃东：控诉新华社四川分社，受成都军区迫害的情况。","index":39,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7d3f5d65a4","type":"paragraph","text":"林：韦等质问我们，为什么要报导成都兵团？要我们报导发行主席著作，说我们配合反革命，小心你们的狗头。","index":40,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"36920cbdcd","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达：今天开到这里，后天再开。","index":41,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0b28964ff5","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}